aawaaj dee hai,aaj yek najar ne,yaa hain ye dil ko gumaan
doharaa rahee hain jaise fajaayen,bhoolee huyee daasataalaut aayee hain fir ruthhee bahaare,kitanaa hasee hain samaa
duniyaa se kah do,naa hum ko pukaare hum kho gaye hain yahaajeewan mein kitanee wiraniyaa thee,chhaayee thee kaisee udaasee
sunakar kisee ke kadamon kee aahat,halachal huyee hain jaraasee
saagar mein jaise lahare uthhee hai,tootee hain khaamoshiyaatufaan mein khoyee kashtee ko aakhir,mil hee gayaa fir kinaaraa
hum chhod aaye khwaabon kee duniyaa,dil ne tere jab pukaaraa
kab se khadee thee baahe pasaare,is dil kee tanahaeeyaaab yaad aayaa,kitanaa adhuraa ab tak thaa dil kaa fasaanaa
yoo saath aa ke,dil mein samaa ke,daaman naa hum se chhudaanaa
jin raasato par tere kadam ho,manjil hain meree wahaa